Package: pgedge-postgres-mcp-kb
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: pgEdge PostgreSQL MCP Knowledge Base
 The pgEdge PostgreSQL MCP Knowledge Base bundles the kb-builder
 binary and a pre-built SQLite knowledgebase of PostgreSQL and pgEdge
 documentation. The pgEdge PostgreSQL MCP Server consumes the
 knowledgebase for semantic search; the kb-builder binary regenerates
 or extends it from configured documentation sources.
